doctype html
html(lang="en")
  head
    include partials/header
  body.login
    .contenedor-formulario
      h1=nombrePagina
      p Agrega tu email para reestablecer tu password.
      form.caja-login(method="POST" action="/reestablecer")
        .campo
          label(for="email") E-mail:
          input(type="text" name="email" placeholder="Tu Email" value= email)
        .campo.enviar
          input.boton(type="submit" value="Reestablecer Password")
        .campo.acciones
          a(href="/iniciar-sesion") Ya me acuerdo, volver a Login.
